ing up?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Amazonite is the most commonly chosen — long tied to honest expression and easing held-back words.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What is the best crystal for public speaking or a presentation?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Lapis lazuli and kyanite — lapis for thoughtful, weighted words, kyanite for calm, steady delivery.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Which crystal helps me listen better in conversations?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Turquoise and chrysocolla — turquoise for warm connection, chrysocolla for the calm that lets you hear.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How should I cleanse communication crystals?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Smoke (sage, palo santo), sound (singing bowl), or moonlight work for most stones. Handle soft pieces gently and keep them dry.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What is the best crystal bracelet for communication?</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">An amazonite bracelet is the most common first choice — easy to wear daily as a reminder to speak gently and clearly.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Explore More Crystal Guides</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-confidence/\">Crystals for Confidence</a></li><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-courage/\">Crystals for Courage</a></li><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-creativity/\">Crystals for Creativity</a></li><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-peace/\">Crystals for Peace</a></li><li><a href=\"/crystals-for-self-love/\">Crystals for Self-love</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Good communication is a practice, not a gift — and a real stone can be a steady cue to speak gently and mean it. Start with one and let small pauses help. For more, explore <a href=\"/personal-empowerment/\">Personal Empowerment</a>.</p>\n",
